commit.message:
Add "type" attribute to library channels (#563)

* Add "type" attribute to library channels

YTMusic Library Channels list not only channels in the narrow sense but also artists publishing podcasts and episodes (e.g. The Offspring). To distinguish the two types of items, the json code contains a page_type attribute. This PR adds code to read the page_type attribute and, if present, add a "tyoe" item with a value of "channel" or "artist" to the artist dictionary object.

* Fix parsing of album and views in parse_playlist_items

* Add "own_playlist" attribute to playlists

To allow for an easy distinction between owned / editable and community / non-editable playlists,in applications incorporating ytmusicapi, a boolean "own_playlist" dictionary entry is added to playlists based on existing code already identifying this property.
